{
  "name": "MAXXAM AI Readiness Scorecard - Quiz Funnel",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "webhook-trigger-001",
      "name": "Quiz Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "position": [
        0,
        300
      ],
      "webhookId": "ai-readiness-quiz-webhook",
      "parameters": {
        "path": "ai-readiness-quiz",
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": {}
      },
      "typeVersion": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-overview-001",
      "name": "Workflow Overview",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -200,
        0
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 4,
        "width": 450,
        "height": 280,
        "content": "## \ud83c\udfaf MAXXAM AI Readiness Scorecard\n### Quiz Funnel \u2014 v2 (custom quiz.html)\n\n**Payload from quiz.html:**\n- firstName, lastName, email, phone\n- overall (0\u2013100%), tier (starter/building/advanced)\n- weakestCategory, categoryScores {visibility,trust,revenue,scale,operations,mindset}\n- industry, revenue, timeline, source\n\n**Flow:**\n1. Receive quiz submission\n2. Parse & normalize payload\n3. Enrich with routing tags\n4. Route \u2192 Hot / Warm / Cool / Cold\n5. Log to Google Sheets\n6. Generate PDF\n7. Email results + booking link\n8. Alert Reggie for hot leads"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "parse-quiz-data-001",
      "name": "Parse Quiz Data",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "position": [
        250,
        300
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// \u2500\u2500 MAXXAM AI \u2014 Redacted Implementation \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\n//\n// Purpose: Normalize and validate the quiz.html POST payload\n// Inputs:  Raw webhook body: email, firstName, lastName, phone, overall(%), tier, categoryScores{}, weakestCategory, industry, revenue, timeline, source, completedAt\n// Outputs: Normalized lead object with standardized field names and defaults\n//\n// This node implements proprietary MAXXAM AI logic.\n// Full implementation is available to MAXXAM AI clients.\n//\n// \u2192 Book a discovery call: https://tinyurl.com/maxxam-call\n// \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\n\nreturn { json: {} }; // stub \u2014 see full implementation\n"
      },
      "typeVersion": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "calculate-score-001",
      "name": "Enrich Lead Data",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "position": [
        500,
        300
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// \u2500\u2500 MAXXAM AI \u2014 Redacted Implementation \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\n//\n// Purpose: Score and tag the lead by readiness tier for downstream routing\n// Inputs:  Normalized lead: overall(%), tier, categoryScores, weakestCategory, industry, revenue, timeline\n// Outputs: categoryTag(hot/warm/cool/cold), emailSequence, primaryCTA, allTags, industryTag, revenueTag, timelineTag\n//\n// This node implements proprietary MAXXAM AI logic.\n// Full implementation is available to MAXXAM AI clients.\n//\n// \u2192 Book a discovery call: https://tinyurl.com/maxxam-call\n// \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\n\nreturn { json: {} }; // stub \u2014 see full implementation\n"
      },
      "typeVersion": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-score-001",
      "name": "Enrich Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        450,
        80
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 5,
        "width": 350,
        "height": 200,
        "content": "### \ud83d\udcca Step 3: Enrich Lead Data\n\n**Maps quiz.html payload to routing fields:**\n- overall % \u2192 tier \u2192 categoryTag\n- industry / revenue / timeline \u2192 tags\n- weakestCategory \u2192 label for PDF\n\n**Tier \u2192 Lead Temp:**\n- advanced (71-100%) \u2192 hot-lead\n- building (46-70%) \u2192 warm-lead\n- starter 26-45% \u2192 cool-lead\n- starter 0-25% \u2192 cold-lead"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "route-by-category-001",
      "name": "Route by Category",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.switch",
      "position": [
        750,
        300
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "rules": {
          "values": [
            {
              "outputKey": "Hot Lead (Advanced)",
              "conditions": {
                "options": {
                  "caseSensitive": true,
                  "typeValidation": "strict"
                },
                "combinator": "and",
                "conditions": [
                  {
                    "operator": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "operation": "equals"
                    },
                    "leftValue": "={{ $json.categoryTag }}",
                    "rightValue": "hot-lead"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "renameOutput": true
            },
            {
              "outputKey": "Warm Lead (Builder)",
              "conditions": {
                "options": {
                  "caseSensitive": true,
                  "typeValidation": "strict"
                },
                "combinator": "and",
                "conditions": [
                  {
                    "id": "warm-condition",
                    "operator": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "operation": "equals"
                    },
                    "leftValue": "={{ $json.categoryTag }}",
                    "rightValue": "warm-lead"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "renameOutput": true
            },
            {
              "outputKey": "Cool Lead (Starter+)",
              "conditions": {
                "options": {
                  "caseSensitive": true,
                  "typeValidation": "strict"
                },
                "combinator": "and",
                "conditions": [
                  {
                    "id": "cool-condition",
                    "operator": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "operation": "equals"
                    },
                    "leftValue": "={{ $json.categoryTag }}",
                    "rightValue": "cool-lead"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "renameOutput": true
            },
            {
              "outputKey": "Cold Lead (Starter)",
              "conditions": {
                "options": {
                  "caseSensitive": true,
                  "typeValidation": "strict"
                },
                "combinator": "and",
                "conditions": [
                  {
                    "id": "cold-condition",
                    "operator": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "operation": "equals"
                    },
                    "leftValue": "={{ $json.categoryTag }}",
                    "rightValue": "cold-lead"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "renameOutput": true
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "fallbackOutput": "extra"
        }
      },
      "typeVersion": 3.2
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-route-001",
      "name": "Routing Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        700,
        180
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 3,
        "width": 300,
        "height": 100,
        "content": "### \ud83d\udd00 Step 4: Route by Score\nDirects leads to appropriate paths based on tier."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
