    {
      "id": "sticky-sheets-001",
      "name": "Google Sheets Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        1200,
        100
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 2,
        "width": 350,
        "height": 200,
        "content": "### \ud83d\udcca Step 5: Log to Google Sheets\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Create Google Sheet\n2. Add tab named: Responses\n3. Row 1 headers match the column list\n4. Connect Google Sheets credentials\n5. Set GOOGLE_SHEET_URL env var\n\n**Columns:** Timestamp, Email, First/Last Name, Phone, Overall %, Tier, Category, 6 category %s, Industry, Revenue Range, Timeline, Source, Tags, Email Sequence"
      },
